title: Lusty Argonian 1
author: Defmork
pages:
#- Volume 1

Act IV, Scene III, continued

§oLifts-Her-Tail:
§rCertainly not, kind sir! I am here but to clean your chambers.

§oCrantius Colto:
§rIs that all you have come here for, 
#- little one? My chambers?

§oLifts-Her-Tail:
§rI have no idea what it is you imply, master. I am but a poor Argonian maid.

§r§oCrantius Colto:
§rSo you are, my dumpling. And a good one at that. 
#- Such strong legs and shapely tail.

§oLifts-Her-Tail:
§rYou embarrass me, sir!

§oCrantius Colto:
§rFear not. You are safe here with me.

§oLifts-Her-Tail:
§rI must finish my cleaning, sir. 
#- The mistress will have my head if I do not!

§oCrantius Colto:
§rCleaning, eh? I have something for you. Here, polish my spear.

§oLifts-Her-Tail:
§rBut it is huge! It could take me all night!
#- §oCrantius Colto
§rPlenty of time, my sweet.
Plenty of time.



End of Act IV, Scene III
#- 